        "id": 5015
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-10-13T12:27:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So I clearly don\u0027t have a good understanding of how d3 works; you\u0027re allowed to exit() without an enter()?",
      "parentUuid": "bc744ebe_19cf4b80",
      "revId": "ff675e00d1e7cf4e23cec1af661fd897f961c2f5",
